election, what does that mean?

02:55.133 --> 02:59.833 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER, The Cook Political
Report: Well, that's just one
more piece of what has been

02:59.833 --> 03:04.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
this never-ending puzzle
called the Russian
impact on this election.

03:06.866 --> 03:10.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And what's difficult about
sifting through all of this,
Judy, it's a little bit like

03:10.333 --> 03:15.333 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
one of those games where
there's a picture made up
of a lot of different tiles.

03:17.266 --> 03:19.733 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
You don't know what that picture
is until you flip over all
the tiles to get the picture.

03:19.733 --> 03:23.600 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And all we're getting the
one tile here and one tile
there and one tile over here.

03:23.600 --> 03:27.500 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
So we have little pieces, but
we don't know what the big
picture is, and I don't know

03:27.500 --> 03:30.033 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
that we're going ever going
to find out the big picture.

03:30.033 --> 03:34.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Then put on top of it all of
the politics around it, whether
it's the president saying

03:34.466 --> 03:39.466 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
he doesn't know really if
the Russians interfered in
this, the push by Democrats
to really politicize

03:41.933 --> 03:46.233 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
