03:49.000 --> 03:52.766 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And now, of course, we have
James Comey, the FBI director,
coming to the Hill to talk more

03:52.766 --> 03:54.833 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
about this Thursday.

03:54.833 --> 03:57.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
