04:24.500 --> 04:28.666 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And, Amy,
there was a lot of speculation
about this, people saying, if

04:28.666 --> 04:31.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
the president did that,
it would be explosive.

04:31.200 --> 04:32.733 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: Absolutely.

04:32.733 --> 04:37.333 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
Let me him go and testify,
and then respond to that.

04:39.233 --> 04:41.300 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
If you block him from testifying
in the first place, the first
thing everybody is going

04:41.300 --> 04:44.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
to say is, well, of course the
White House has something to
hide, that's why they don't

04:44.066 --> 04:46.100 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
want him to testify.

04:46.100 --> 04:48.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: So, let's go
back, Tam, to this other story
we have been dealing with

04:48.700 --> 04:52.700 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
