of tweets that you just
heard John Yang reporting

04:52.700 --> 04:57.700 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
on from the president today,
basically doubling down on his
original travel ban, saying, I

04:59.766 --> 05:01.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
