05:08.066 --> 05:10.166 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Is that
a serious question?

05:10.166 --> 05:11.866 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

05:11.866 --> 05:15.266 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Lawyers
