Kellyanne Conway, said
in a series of tweets,
basically, the president's

05:31.966 --> 05:35.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
tweets may make people
feel good, but they are
not helping his legal case.

05:35.033 --> 05:40.033 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
Also, the lawyer who is
representing Hawaii in one of
these cases that has led to the

05:41.933 --> 05:46.200 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
