essentially said, wow,
thank you, President Trump.

05:46.200 --> 05:47.766 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
You're certainly helping us.

05:47.766 --> 05:48.800 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
