going to be co-counsel.

05:48.800 --> 05:50.900 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(LAUGHTER)

05:50.900 --> 05:54.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
AMY WALTER: And that's what
-- part of the reason that the
courts didn't enact the travel

05:56.766 --> 06:00.900 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
ban in the first place was
based on statements that Trump
made on the campaign trail.

06:02.933 --> 06:06.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
