attention to the tweets.

06:43.433 --> 06:44.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
TAMARA KEITH: Right.

06:44.433 --> 06:46.400 align:left position:37.5%,start line:93.33% size:62.5%
