06:46.400 --> 06:47.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: That you
should be focused on what the
president is getting done.

06:47.866 --> 06:49.800 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Yes, why focus
on the tweets, she says.

06:49.800 --> 06:51.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
