of the United States says
something, it matters.

06:54.666 --> 06:59.666 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
Now, sometimes, his
statements come on letterhead
from the White House that
say this is an official

07:01.133 --> 07:03.100 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
statement of the president
of the United States.

07:03.100 --> 07:07.066 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
But the reality is that,
often, he goes on Twitter and
contradicts the things that are

07:07.066 --> 07:09.133 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
on the official letterhead.

07:09.133 --> 07:13.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
And, really, his tweets are this
unprecedented access to what
is in the mind of the president

07:15.466 --> 07:16.466 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
of the United States.

07:16.466 --> 07:18.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
It is unfiltered.

07:18.133 --> 07:22.133 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
