07:23.666 --> 07:25.933 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
And she said, I don't think so.

07:25.933 --> 07:28.933 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
So, actually, this is
what the president thinks.

07:28.933 --> 07:31.000 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: And says.

07:31.000 --> 07:33.200 align:left position:12.5%,start line:73.33% size:87.5%
And it shouldn't be any
different if he says
it on Twitter than if
he says it at a press

07:33.200 --> 07:35.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
conference or if he
sent something on
official letterhead.

07:35.433 --> 07:38.866 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: And I should
say we at the "NewsHour" view
the tweets as another form

07:38.866 --> 07:40.900 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
