president, from the White House.

07:40.900 --> 07:41.900 align:left position:12.5%,start line:93.33% size:87.5%
AMY WALTER: Absolutely.

07:41.900 --> 07:43.100 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
Absolutely.

07:43.100 --> 07:44.600 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: There
are official statements.

07:44.600 --> 07:45.533 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
