07:47.366 --> 07:48.833 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

07:48.833 --> 07:49.766 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
AMY WALTER: And Twitter is
another one of those methods.

07:49.766 --> 07:50.533 align:left position:0%,start line:93.33% size:100%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Twitter is...

07:50.533 --> 07:51.800 align:left position:25%,start line:93.33% size:75%
(CROSSTALK)

07:51.800 --> 07:54.433 align:left position:12.5%,start line:86.67% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: ...
of communicating.

07:54.433 --> 07:57.100 align:left position:0%,start line:73.33% size:100%
AMY WALTER: And everything
he says as a private -
- when he was a private
citizen is very different

07:57.100 --> 07:59.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
