08:04.200 --> 08:06.266 align:left position:0%,start line:86.67% size:100%
It carries the weight of being
the leader of this country.

08:06.266 --> 08:08.466 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
TAMARA KEITH: Though I think
