watching, including leaders
from around the world.

08:22.666 --> 08:26.633 align:left position:12.5%,start line:80% size:87.5%
JUDY WOODRUFF: Everybody
is watching who focuses
on this administration.

08:26.633 --> 08:30.800 align:left position:0%,start line:80% size:100%
